April 8, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: I served the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, for ten years. By Allah, he never even said to me, \u201cUff!\u201d He never said harshly, \u201cWhy did you do that?\u201d or, \u201cWhy did you not do that?\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6038, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2309 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11519,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/18\/do-not-curse-insult-sahabah\/","url_meta":{"origin":2529,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: Do not curse companions of the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not insult my companions. If one of you were to spend the likes of mount Uhud in gold, it would not reach a small portion of theirs or even half of that.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3673,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6565,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/17\/jihad-hajj-mabrur-best-iman\/","url_meta":{"origin":2529,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Struggle: Jihad, Hajj among best deeds after faith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace an